### Request Context Examples
### Run server first: go run .

### 1. Query Parameters - c.Req.QueryParam()
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hello?name=John

###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hello
# Uses default value "Guest"

### 2. Path Parameters - c.Req.PathParam()
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/123

###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/alice

### 3. Body Binding - c.Req.BindBody()
POST http://localhost:8080/api/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "age": 25
}

###
POST http://localhost:8080/api/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bo",
  "age": 25
}
# Validation error: name min=3

###
POST http://localhost:8080/api/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "age": 150
}
# Validation error: age max=120

### 4. Smart Binding - c.Req.BindAll() (path + query + header + body)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/update/99?page=2
Authorization: Bearer token123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "age": 30
}

###
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/update/88?page=5
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Charlie"
}
# Missing Authorization header (but won't fail binding)

### 5. Response Types - c.Resp vs c.Api

# c.Resp.Json - Custom structure
GET http://localhost:8080/

###
# c.Resp.Html - HTML response
GET http://localhost:8080/admin

###
# c.Api.Ok - Standard API response
GET http://localhost:8080/api/list

### 6. API Error Responses - c.Api.*

# 404 Not Found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/error?type=notfound

###
# 400 Bad Request
GET http://localhost:8080/api/error?type=badrequest

###
# 401 Unauthorized
GET http://localhost:8080/api/error?type=unauthorized

###
# 403 Forbidden
GET http://localhost:8080/api/error?type=forbidden

###
# 500 Internal Error
GET http://localhost:8080/api/error?type=internal

###
# Custom status code
GET http://localhost:8080/api/error?type=teapot

### 7. Context Storage - c.Set() and c.Value()

# Without Authorization header - will fail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/profile

###
# With Authorization header - will succeed
GET http://localhost:8080/api/profile
Authorization: Bearer token123

### 8. Middleware Chain - c.Next()

# Logging middleware wraps the handler
GET http://localhost:8080/api/slow
# Check server logs for timing

### 9. Direct HTTP Access - c.R and c.W

GET http://localhost:8080/api/info
User-Agent: MyCustomAgent/1.0

### 10. Welcome Page
GET http://localhost:8080/
